1. Purchase the stock in bulk when its value is low. 
2. For daily transaction, purchase the stock when it the below the Opening value and sell it when price is above the Opening value. 
3. For Weekly transaction, 
when the stock price is 300 purchase 400 stock, 
when the stock price is 295 purchase 400 stock. 
When the stock price is 290 purchase 800 stock 
when the stock price is 285 purchase 800 stock.
when the stock price is 280 purchase 1600 stock. 

Sell the stock if the price difference is Rs 10. 


